tags.name: The Villages at Turning Stone RV Park

tags.description:
Multiple pull-off locations available along Sterling Road.

Throughout November 1st until April 1st, parking is prohibited on Sterling Road from 2 a.m. until 6 a.m.
You are not allowed to park on Sterling Road for more than 12 hours at a time.
tags.name: Pull-Off Area on Sterling Road
tags.note:
Cell reception is okay with 2-3 bars 5G on T-Mobile's Network.

No signs stating: "No Camping", "No Overnight Parking", or "No Parking".
